    Packages
    Package
    Description
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3
    This meta-package contains all the packages used to run the Archive Server application.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.configs
    This package contains configurations used to customize the Spring Boot server running.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.controllers
    This package contains all controllers used by the Archive Server.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.core
    This package holds the core AO3 ingestion logic for the application.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.exceptions
    This package contains the exceptions used by the Archive Server backend.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.models
    This package contains the data models the Archive Server application uses to handle server data.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.repositories
    This package defines the entities (table entry) and the repositories (databases) the Archive Server application uses to store persistent data.
    com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.services
    This package contains the services that run the logic for the Archive Server application.
